CREATE  OR REPLACE TABLE StudentRecords (
    RecordID INT PRIMARY KEY ,  -- Unique identifier for each record
    StudentName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,       -- Name of the student
    Subject VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,           -- Subject of the exam
    Marks INT NOT NULL,                      -- Marks obtained by the student
    Year INT NOT NULL                        -- Year in which the marks were obtained
);
